    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "At Lat. 28°13' N. Long.\n177°22' I.\n(Pacific\nOcean),\non Midway Island,\nare these strange\nbirds,\nthe gonies,\n(Laysan Albatross). Tame,\ndark, juzzy-feathered baby gonies cluster by the\nthousands on the sands of this coral island,\nunique stopping point on Pan American Air-\nways 9,000-mile transpacific airline.\nshake to\nTanh\nMIDWAY ISLAND.\nAPR\nSARCARDS\nUNITE\nPOSTAGE\nADDRES\n110 CENTS 10\nLes Litota\nHaurent Clue\nYa Bogal\nШки\n4.1А\nVia cleane- stashula"
